uri : https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uniform_resource_identifier
regexp : Regular expression.

Function name  						Description
-------------						-----------

urlToFilename(uri)					Extracting a filename from a uri.
getHostname(uri)					Extracting a hostname from a uri.
link_sherlock(url, regexp, user_agent)			Searching in a html after links that match a given regexp.
downl_f(file_uri, downl_path)				Downloading a file and write it to a given path.
downl_all(array_w_links, dwl_path)			Downloading a array with links to a given path.
if_doublet(file_n, cmp_a)				Checking a doublet in a directory. (Needs to fix?)
yesno()							Check whether the user want to do something or not.

